Class NfsType

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.emc.ecs.nfsclient.nfs.NfsType

  • public class NfsType
extends java.lang.Object
    Enums for the NFS file types, as specified by RFC 1813 (https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc1813).
